  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>I've attached a patch addressing the missing paragraph breaks, plus a test. Two
other commits clean up unused imports and variables and remove trailing
whitespace. (paulproteus: if you'd prefer that I not do this cosmetic clean-up,
or if I'm not keeping with style guidelines OpenHatch has, please let me know --
I didn't see a style document on the wiki)

As an aside, after following the README instructions I seem to have an
environment in which many tests fail. I've attached the output from
test_sans_customs and the search tests as examples, in case that's useful. I did
verify that no new tests failed after adding these commits.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
  <tr>
   <th><a href="msg413">msg413 (view)</a></th>
